= Color Scheme =

This page allows to customize the color schemes of the UI.

== Primary Colors ==

The following color scheme configuration can be used to change the appearance of the UI.

* Note: The cache of the browser needs to be refreshed such that the changes take effect (Hint: press Ctrl + F5).

<div style="float:left;">
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.admin.InlineConfigurationWidget | 
 configOptions = {{ 'ui.color.primaryBackground' | 'ui.color.secondaryBackground' | 'ui.color.contrastColor' | 'ui.color.secondaryContrastColor' | 'ui.header.logo' }}
 | fields = {{ 'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
}}
{{#widget: CodeExecution | 
 clazz = 'com.fluidops.iwb.util.UIUtil'
 | method = 'resetColorScheme'
 | passContext = true
 | render = 'btn'
 | label = 'Reset'
}}
</div>

<div style="float:left;margin-top:15px;">
	<table style="margin:0px;margin-left:20px">
		<caption><b>Preview</b></caption>
		<tr>
			<td style="margin:1px;"><div class="previewPrimaryBackground" style="width:25px; height:25px; border: 1px solid black;">&nbsp;</div></td>
			<td style="vertical-align:middle;"><div class="valuePrimaryBackground">Value: </div></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="margin:1px;"><div class="previewSecondaryBackground" style="width:25px; height:25px; border: 1px solid black;">&nbsp;</div></td>
			<td style="vertical-align:middle;"><div class="valueSecondaryBackground">Value: </div></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="margin:1px;"><div class="previewContrastColor" style="width:25px; height:25px; border: 1px solid black;">&nbsp;</div></td>
			<td style="vertical-align:middle;"><div class="valueContrastColor">Value: </div></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="margin:1px;"><div class="previewSecondaryContrastColor" style="width:25px; height:25px; border: 1px solid black;">&nbsp;</div></td>
			<td style="vertical-align:middle;"><div class="valueSecondaryContrastColor">Value: </div></td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</div>
<div style="clear:both;/"><br>

== Chart Colors ==

The following color scheme configuration can be used to change the default colors for charts.

Hint: See [[Help:ChartCustomization]] for additional customization options.

<div style="float:left;">
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.ecm.widget.InlineConfigurationWidget | 
 fields = {{ 'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
 | configOptions = {{ 'chartColorLow' | 'chartColorHigh' }}
}}
{{#widget: CodeExecution | 
 clazz = 'com.fluidops.iwb.util.UIUtil'
 | method = 'resetChartColors'
 | passContext = true
 | render = 'btn'
 | label = 'Reset'
}}
</div>

<div style="float:left;margin-top:15px;">
	<table style="margin:0px;margin-left:20px">
		<caption><b>Preview</b></caption>
		<tr>
			<td>
				{{#widget: PieChart | 
				 output = {{ 'y1' }}
				 | input = 'x'
				 | styling = 
				   {{ width = '300'
				    | height = '300'
				   }}
				 | query = 'SELECT * WHERE {  
				 VALUES (?x ?y1 ?y2) {
					( "Low"  "10" "5")
					( "Mixed"  "20" "10" )
					( "High"  "30" "15" )
				}
				}'
				}}
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</div>
<div style="clear:both;/">

Change the 8 chart scheme colors. This is applicable for the charts that use the corresponding color variables in their settings file.

<div style="float:left;">
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.ecm.widget.InlineConfigurationWidget | 
 fields = {{ 'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
 | configOptions = {{ 'ui.color.schemeColor1' | 'ui.color.schemeColor2' | 'ui.color.schemeColor3' | 'ui.color.schemeColor4' | 'ui.color.schemeColor5' | 'ui.color.schemeColor6' | 'ui.color.schemeColor7' | 'ui.color.schemeColor8'}}
}}
{{#widget: CodeExecution | 
 clazz = 'com.fluidops.iwb.util.UIUtil'
 | method = 'resetChartSchemeColors'
 | passContext = true
 | render = 'btn'
 | label = 'Reset'
}}
</div>

<div style="float:left;margin-top:15px;">
