= Header Logo =

In the following the logo that is rendered in the header and on the login screen respectively can be customized. 

Note that for positioning reasons the logos should have the following dimensions:
* Login logo: <i>150 x 22 px</i>
* Header logo: <i>250 x 90 px</i> (maximum values, actual logo can be smaller)
Also note that the login logo must be located in the ''login'' folder of the {{PRODUCT}} installation.

<div style="float:left;">
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.ecm.widget.InlineConfigurationWidget | 
 fields = {{ 'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
 | configOptions = {{  'ui.logo.path' | 'ui.loginLogo.path'}}
}}
{{#widget: CodeExecution | 
 clazz = 'com.fluidops.iwb.util.UIUtil'
 | method = 'resetLogos'
 | passContext = true
 | render = 'btn'
 | label = 'Reset'
}}
</div>

<div style="float:left;margin-top:15px;">
	<table style="margin:0px;margin-left:20px">
		<tr>
			<td> <center><b>Header Logo Preview</b></center> </td>
			<td>  <center><b>Login Logo Preview</b></center> </td>
 		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td><div class="headerLogoPreview"></div></td>
			<td><div class="loginLogoPreview"></div></td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</div>
